videos.description: Kellen Mond finds Jalen Wydermyer wide open for a touchdown to put Texas A&M ahead 14-0 vs. South Carolina.

videos.headline: Wydermyer trots in for 15-yard Texas A&M TD

videos.description: Kellen Mond puts on a passing clinic as he throws four touchdowns, while running for a fifth in Texas A&M's 48-3 win vs. South Carolina.

videos.headline: Kellen Mond records 5 TDs in blowout win vs. South Carolina

videos.description: Texas A&M coach Jimbo Fisher praises the complete performance of his team and quarterback Kellen Mond in a 48-3 win over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Fisher lauds Aggies' defense, QB Mond's play

videos.description: The No. 7 Texas A&M defense holds South Carolina to 150 total yards and forces two turnovers, allowing the offense plenty of opportunity.
videos.headline: Aggies dominate both sides of ball in 48-3 victory
